channel.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube Channel of SET Solution.
You can also follow us on Twitter http://twitter.com/setsolution & Facebook http://facebook.com/setsolution

Who’s behind SET Solution?
SET Solution is the personal showcase of Federico Fiore: he’s in the freelance VFX production since 2011 and he’s the curator of the YouTube Channel “SET Solution”.
He’s a 3D\VFX Generalist, his videos on Youtube have reached over 25 millions views and he has worked with some companies in Italy and Europe.

*** For business inquiries, copyright information and to share our videos, please send us an email: http://setsolution.it/#contact  ***
